#VenmoPartner We're officially in the final countdown for baby boy's arrival! Can't believe he's coming in just a few short weeks. This summer, we're using @venmo for our nursery renovations & to get everything we need for little man haha. What summer projects could you use extra money for?!? New users who download and sign up using my link can get $10 to help bring your adventure to life! Bonus points for letting me know in the comments + your Venmo handle (without the @) what you’re using Venmo to achieve!
Offer ends 8/31/2021. Terms apply; https://bit.ly/Shawn-10
